@startuml
title Nested swimlanes with parallel forks
|Customer|
start
:Submit order;
|Warehouse|
:Receive order notification;
fork
  |Warehouse|
  :Pick items;
  :Pack items;
fork again
  |Finance|
  :Charge payment;
  if (payment ok?) then (yes)
    :Issue receipt;
  else (no)
    :Notify customer;
    detach
  endif
end fork
|Logistics|
:Assign courier;
:Print label;
fork
  |Logistics|
  :Hand off to courier;
fork again
  |Warehouse|
  :Update inventory;
end fork
|Customer|
:Receive delivery notification;
stop
@enduml
